                <div id="applets"><br>
                  <h3>Applets</h3>
                  <p class="big-paragraph">Generating dynamic vis assets for use in our ABR program may be a barrier for artists unfamiliar with programming architectures. We created a series of Applets—ColorLoom, Infinite Line, Glyph Aligner, and Texture Mapper—to facilitate asset creation and easy import in ABR.  </p>
